## ⚡ Quick Start (30 minutes)

### 1. Create Folder Structure (5 min)
```bash
mkdir UFCFFY-15-M-CSA-Portfolio
cd UFCFFY-15-M-CSA-Portfolio

# Copy all artifacts I provided into appropriate locations
```

### 2. Setup Python Environment (10 min)
```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
# OR
venv\Scripts\activate     # Windows

pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Add Your Data (5 min)
```bash
# Move your log file
cp /path/to/p2-pitta_25sept.txt activity1-log-analysis/data/

# Download DGA dataset from Blackboard
# Place in activity2-dga-classification/data/
```

### 4. Test Setup (10 min)
```bash
# Start Jupyter
jupyter notebook

# Open Activity 1 notebook
# Run first few cells to verify data loads
```

